\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"en-GB\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(473,79,1,'','2013-12-28 15:07:36',591,2684,'f088d9796e3b15fa6c41f3167b980f4020a3c6e3','{\"id\":79,\"asset_id\":\"187\",\"title\":\"AROMATIC PLANTS\",\"alias\":\"prodotto-25\",\"introtext\":\"<p>\\r\\nAromatic herbs from Albenga are known all over the world for their beneficial properties, their scent and their taste.\\r\\n \\r\\nEvery year millions of aromatic herbs with decorative, therapeutic and beneficial properties are grown in Albenga.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nMankind has always used aromatic herbs for medicinal use, they are natural chemical laboratories and each plants has its properties and its specific use.\\r\\n \\r\\nIn gardens and balconies many spaces are dedicated to aromatic herbs today, to exalt their ornamental characteristics besides their cooking properties.\\r\\n \\r\\nTogether with the classic aromatic herbs we can supply different kinds of special aromatics such as rocket and lemon verbena.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nOur range of aromatic herbs includes:\\r\\n- Lavander\\r\\n- Lemon verbena\\r\\n- Oregano\\r\\n- Parsley\\r\\n- Sage\\r\\n- Mint\\r\\n- Rosemary\\r\\n- Thyme\\r\\n- Cotton lavander\\r\\n- Winter savory\\r\\n- Sweet marjoram\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n{gallery}aromi:150:150:0:0{\\/gallery}\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"11\",\"created\":\"2013-12-08 21:27:08\",\"created_by\":\"591\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2013-12-28 15:07:36\",\"modified_by\":\"591\",\"checked_out\":\"591\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2013-12-28 15:06:46\",\"publish_up\":\"2013-12-08 21:27:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":fal